            "query": "FROM logs-azure.microsoft_365* | KEEP `@timestamp`, `azure.microsoft_365.workload`, `azure.microsoft_365.record_type`, `azure.microsoft_365.user_id`, `azure.microsoft_365.result`, `azure.microsoft_365.client_ip` | SORT `@timestamp` DESC | LIMIT 100"
